Itu cabang dari telkom university di bandung.  Mereka memiliki program yang mencakup mata pelajaran yang berkaitan dengan industri perangkat lunak dan perangkat keras.  Resepsionis pusat informasi kampus Surabaya harus lebih interaktif dengan orang tua siswa yang datang jauh untuk menanyakan program dan fasilitas di Universitas.  Mereka mengabaikan pelanggan dan mengerjakan laptop mereka.  Pemimpin program juga harus mengetahui informasi terkini tentang kurikulum, program, dan karier siswa mereka sendiri.  Beruntung ada tenaga pengajar yang rajin membantu kami memberikan informasi mengenai program dan fasilitas.It's the branch of the telkom university in Bandung. They have programs covering subjects related to the software and hardware industry. The receptionist at the information center in Surabaya campus has to be more interactive with the parents when they come from long way to enquire about the programs and facilities at the University. They ignore the customer and work on their laptops. Program leaders must also be up to date about their own curriculum, programs, and student careers. Luckily there was a teaching staff who could diligently help us give information about the programs and facilities.Itu cabang dari telkom university di bandung.
